# Theme & UI System

## Token object: `islandTheme` (apps/web/src/theme.ts)
```ts
islandTheme.color.*        // CSS var refs: appBg, panelBg, panelMutedBg, textPrimary/secondary/muted/subtle/inverted,
                           // border, cardBorder, primary, primaryText, primaryStrong, primaryGlow,
                           // secondary, info, infoText, toolAccent, danger, dangerSurface, dangerText, success, successText
islandTheme.radius.*       // control(10px), card(12px), surface(14px)
islandTheme.spacing.*      // cardPadding, pagePaddingWide, pagePaddingNarrow
islandTheme.layout.*       // appMaxWidth(1200), authMaxWidth(900), proseMaxWidth(68ch)
islandTheme.glass.*        // blur, blurStrong, edge
islandTheme.motion.dur.*   // fast, med, slow, ambient
islandTheme.motion.ease.*  // out, inOut, spring
islandTheme.font.*         // display, body, mono (full font-family stacks)
islandTheme.shadow.*       // tileIdle, tileComingSoon, tileGameNightHover, tileToolsHover, toast
islandTheme.gradient.*     // gameNightTile, toolsTile, comingSoonTile
```

## CSS variables (`--bi-*` prefix)
Injected by `SceneGlobalStyles` in `IslandSceneShell`:
- Night values on `:root` by default
- Day values on `:root[data-theme="day"]`

`useDayNight` sets `document.documentElement.dataset.theme` on toggle. Components stay token-driven — never hardcode colors that have a `--bi-*` equivalent.

## Day/night context (apps/web/src/scene/useDayNight.tsx)
```ts
const { mode, toggle, set, isTransitioning } = useDayNight()
// mode: "day" | "night"  — persisted to localStorage key "island.theme"
// isTransitioning: true for ~2.4s after toggle (coordinates sun/moon dip animation)
```
Toggle lives in `UserMenu`. Don't add a second toggle elsewhere.

## islandUi primitives (apps/web/src/islandUi.tsx)
Prefer these before writing inline one-off styled elements:
| Export | Use for |
|--------|---------|
| `IslandButton` | Any action button (variant: primary / secondary / danger) |
| `IslandCard` | Glass panel container (as: section / div / article) |
| `IslandTileButton` | Large image CTA tiles (game-night, tools) |
| `IslandMemberChip` | Pill toggle for member selection |
| `IslandGameCard` | Compact game row with image fallback |
| `IslandGameBlade` | Rich game row — **dead/unused; voting UI lingers in the def but nothing imports it, slated for removal** |
| `IslandComingSoonTile` | Dashed placeholder tile |
| `IslandActiveMemberRow` | Avatar + name + presence row |
| `IslandStatusPill` | Success / danger pill badge |
| `islandCardStyle` | Raw card `CSSProperties` for inline use |
| `islandInputStyle` | Raw input `CSSProperties` for inline use |

## Global utility classes
`.island-display` → Bricolage Grotesque display font  
`.island-mono` → JetBrains Mono

## Scene shell (apps/web/src/scene/IslandSceneShell.tsx)
Fixed full-viewport backdrop behind all content (`zIndex: -10`). Contains: sky gradient, stars/clouds, sun/moon with arc-dip animation, ocean wave band, beach band, vignette. Left/right palm SVGs with scroll parallax. Do not duplicate scene elements inside pages.
